    <introduction>
    <title>Surface Area </title>
    <p>
        Surface area is the total area of the exposed or outer surfaces of a prism.
    </p>
    <p>
        ğŸ”¹A right prism is a geometric solid that has a polygon as its base and vertical faces perpendicular to the base.
